(13, 1, '2015-02-24 20:54:11', '2015-02-24 20:54:11', 'Global Exteriors has been serving Saskatoon since 1994. Over the years, owners and brothers Brian and Andy Fehr have grown the business from a few small teams to managing more than a dozen crews. With more than 20 years spent working in Saskatoon, we have long relationships with some of the top home builders in the city.\r\n\r\nOur specialty is residential exteriors: new and renovated, multi-family and single home. We are experts in siding and soffit, windows and doors, and eavestroughs and insulation. But if you need exterior work done outside our expertise -- like stonework, roofing, or building an addition -- we have access to companies we trust who can finish the job.\r\n\r\nAndy and Brian started in the housing industry working with their dad, and they stayed in the family line of work. Brian worked in siding installation for 15 years before starting Global Exteriors with Andy. Their time on the ground has given them a product knowledge that''s hard to beat. Global Exteriors only provides the best products on the market.\r\n\r\nWe ensure quality workmanship through careful oversight. A foreman visits our sites daily, and every site is inspected by either Andy or Brian upon completion. We also have a full time service person available to answer any questions once the work is done.\r\n<h3>COMMUNITY OUTREACH</h3>\r\nGlobal Exteriors is a community-minded company; we want to improve the quality of both the homes we work on, and the neighbourhoods where our clients live. To that end, we support <a href="http://yfcsask.com/">Youth for Christ Saskatoon</a>, the local chapter of a worldwide Christian movement. Andy has sat on the YFC Sask board of directors for more than a decade, helping to organize tons of fun experiences and activities for kids, including our newest initiative, the <a href="http://yfcsask.com/mobile-youth-centre">Mobile Youth Centre</a>.', 'About', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'about', '', '', '2015-03-15 20:41:55', '2015-03-15 20:41:55', '', 0, 'http://localhost/global-exteriors/?page_id=13', 0, 'page', '', 0),
