(15, 1, '2015-02-24 20:54:16', '2015-02-24 20:54:16', 'Whether we’re doing the installation ourselves or helping you DIY, Global Exteriors only offers the best products. We have access to a wide variety of suppliers, tapping Canada’s top brands to outfit your home’s exterior.\r\n<h3>SERVICES</h3>\r\n<div class="services-page">\r\n<div class="services-grid">\r\n\r\n<img src="http://localhost/global-exteriors/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/services-soffit.jpg" alt="services-soffit" />\r\n<div class="services-grid--content">\r\n<h5>VINYL SIDING</h5>\r\nThe popular choice among today’s consumers, vinyl siding requires little maintenance and is ideal for Saskatchewan’s tough climate.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="services-grid">\r\n\r\n<img src="http://localhost/global-exteriors/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/services-soffit.jpg" alt="services-soffit" />\r\n<div class="services-grid--content">\r\n<h5>SOFFIT, FASCIA, AND TRIM</h5>\r\nA vital element to any home’s appearance, our top-quality soffit, fascia, and trim products add that perfect finishing touch.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="services-grid">\r\n\r\n<img src="http://localhost/global-exteriors/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/services-soffit.jpg" alt="services-soffit" />\r\n<div class="services-grid--content">\r\n<h5>WINDOWS AND DOORS</h5>\r\nEnhance the look of your home while improving energy efficiency. We can provide any style you want for your home.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="services-grid">\r\n\r\n<img src="http://localhost/global-exteriors/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/services-soffit.jpg" alt="services-soffit" />\r\n<div class="services-grid--content">\r\n<h5>EAVESTROUGHS</h5>\r\nAll of our eavestroughs are expertly crafted in-house in a wide range of colours and sizes to suit all of your needs.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>PRODUCTS</h3>\r\n<p>Global Exteriors has access to the best available products through our long standing relationships with our suppliers Gentek, Kaycan, and Mitten.</p>\r\n<div class="products-grid">\r\n\r\n<img src="http://localhost/global-exteriors/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/kaycan-logo.jpg" alt="kaycan-logo" />\r\n<h5>KAYCAN</h5>\r\nTimberlake siding\r\nDaVinci siding\r\nHardwood Valley\r\nRichmond Ultra\r\nKWP engineered wood siding\r\nKWP wood trims\r\nPerfection shingle shakes\r\nVertical and board and batten siding\r\nEco siding engineered wood siding\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="products-grid">\r\n\r\n<img src="http://localhost/global-exteriors/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/gentek-logo.jpg" alt="gentek-logo" />\r\n<h5>GENTEK</h5>\r\nDriftwood siding\r\nSequoia siding\r\nNorthern Forest Elite siding\r\nProdigy siding\r\nBoard and batten siding\r\nAllura siding\r\nHardie board siding\r\nFoundry shakes\r\nLongboard aluminum siding and soffit\r\nGentek windows &amp; doors\r\nVersetta stone faux cement stone panels\r\nRockford stone faux stone panels\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="products-grid">\r\n\r\n<img src="http://localhost/global-exteriors/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/mitten-logo.png" alt="mitten-logo" />\r\n<h5>MITTEN</h5>\r\nSentry siding\r\nHighland siding\r\nCambridge siding\r\nOregon pride siding\r\nSouthern beaded siding\r\nVertical and board and batten siding\r\nInsuplank\r\nGenstone faux stone panels\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Services & Products', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'services', '', '', '2015-03-17 16:46:34', '2015-03-17 16:46:34', '', 0, 'http://localhost/global-exteriors/?page_id=15', 0, 'page', '', 0),
