(818, 1, '2015-03-11 19:39:16', '2015-03-11 19:39:16', 'SERVICES AND PRODUCTS\r\n\r\nWhether we’re doing the installation ourselves or helping you DIY, Global Exteriors only offers the best products. We have access to a wide variety of suppliers, tapping Canada’s top brands to outfit your home’s exterior.\r\n<h3>SERVICES</h3>\r\nVINYL SIDING\r\nThe popular choice among today’s consumers, vinyl siding requires little maintenance and is ideal for Saskatchewan’s tough climate.\r\n\r\nSOFFIT, FASCIA, AND TRIM\r\nA vital element to any home’s appearance, our top-quality soffit, fascia, and trim products add that perfect finishing touch.\r\n\r\nWINDOWS AND DOORS\r\nEnhance the look of your home while improving energy efficiency. We can provide any style you want for your home.\r\n\r\nEAVESTROUGHS\r\nAll of our eavestroughs are expertly crafted in-house in a wide range of colours and sizes to suit all of your needs.\r\n\r\n[HEADER] PRODUCTS\r\n\r\n[SUB-HEAD] KAYCAN\r\nTimberlake siding\r\nDaVinci siding\r\nHardwood Valley\r\nRichmond Ultra\r\nKWP engineered wood siding\r\nKWP wood trims\r\nPerfection shingle shakes\r\nVertical and board and batten siding\r\nEco siding engineered wood siding\r\n\r\n[SUB-HEAD] GENTEK\r\nDriftwood siding\r\nSequoia siding\r\nNorthern Forest Elite siding\r\nProdigy siding\r\nBoard and batten siding\r\nAllura siding\r\nHardie board siding\r\nFoundry shakes\r\nLongboard aluminum siding and soffit\r\nGentek windows &amp; doors\r\nVersetta stone faux cement stone panels\r\nRockford stone faux stone panels\r\n\r\n[SUB-HEAD] MITTEN\r\nSentry siding\r\nHighland siding\r\nCambridge siding\r\nOregon pride siding\r\nSouthern beaded siding\r\nVertical and board and batten siding\r\nInsuplank\r\nGenstone faux stone panels', 'Services & Products', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '15-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-03-11 19:39:16', '2015-03-11 19:39:16', '', 15, 'http://localhost/global-exteriors/15-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
