(880, 1, '2015-03-16 00:15:48', '2015-03-16 00:15:48', 'Whether we’re doing the installation ourselves or helping you DIY, Global Exteriors only offers the best products. We have access to a wide variety of suppliers, tapping Canada’s top brands to outfit your home’s exterior.\r\n<h3>SERVICES</h3>\r\n<div class="services-page">\r\n<div class="services-grid">\r\n<h5>VINYL SIDING</h5>\r\nThe popular choice among today’s consumers, vinyl siding requires little maintenance and is ideal for Saskatchewan’s tough climate.\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="services-grid">\r\n<h5>SOFFIT, FASCIA, AND TRIM</h5>\r\nA vital element to any home’s appearance, our top-quality soffit, fascia, and trim products add that perfect finishing touch.\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="services-grid">\r\n<h5>WINDOWS AND DOORS</h5>\r\nEnhance the look of your home while improving energy efficiency. We can provide any style you want for your home.\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="services-grid">\r\n<h5>EAVESTROUGHS</h5>\r\nAll of our eavestroughs are expertly crafted in-house in a wide range of colours and sizes to suit all of your needs.\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<h3>PRODUCTS</h3>\r\n<div class="products-grid">\r\n<h5>KAYCAN</h5>\r\nTimberlake siding\r\nDaVinci siding\r\nHardwood Valley\r\nRichmond Ultra\r\nKWP engineered wood siding\r\nKWP wood trims\r\nPerfection shingle shakes\r\nVertical and board and batten siding\r\nEco siding engineered wood siding\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="products-grid">\r\n<h5>GENTEK</h5>\r\nDriftwood siding\r\nSequoia siding\r\nNorthern Forest Elite siding\r\nProdigy siding\r\nBoard and batten siding\r\nAllura siding\r\nHardie board siding\r\nFoundry shakes\r\nLongboard aluminum siding and soffit\r\nGentek windows &amp; doors\r\nVersetta stone faux cement stone panels\r\nRockford stone faux stone panels\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="products-grid">\r\n<h5>MITTEN</h5>\r\nSentry siding\r\nHighland siding\r\nCambridge siding\r\nOregon pride siding\r\nSouthern beaded siding\r\nVertical and board and batten siding\r\nInsuplank\r\nGenstone faux stone panels\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Services & Products', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '15-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-03-16 00:15:48', '2015-03-16 00:15:48', '', 15, 'http://localhost/global-exteriors/15-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(881, 1, '2015-03-16 00:16:57', '2015-03-16 00:16:57', '[caption id="attachment_835" align="alignright" width="500"]<img class="wp-image-835 size-medium" src="http://localhost/global-exteriors/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/showroom-pics-500x333.jpg" alt="showroom pics" width="500" height="333" /> Compellingly innovate 24/365 imperatives rather than ethical.[/caption]\r\n\r\nAre you ready to DIY? Installing siding yourself can save you money, but before you embark on a project check your skill level: Do you feel confident? Have you done projects like this before? Are you a naturally handy or crafty person?\r\n\r\nIf so, great! The next step is preparation. Vinyl siding is the best choice for do-it-yourself projects because it''s easier to remove, alter, and reinstall than any other type of siding, and the only special tool you''ll need for the job is an unlocking tool, or zip tool.\r\n\r\nWe have some great sources to help guide you through the process:\r\nGentek Vinyl Products Installation Guide [LINK TO PDF]\r\nKaycan Vinyl Siding Estimating and Installation Guide [LINK TO PDF]\r\nMitten How to Install Guide: Prepare, Install &amp; Care for your New Vinyl Siding [LINK TO PDF]\r\n\r\nOnce you have a plan in place, you''ll need to choose the right materials. That''s where the experts at Global Exteriors come in. We have a full range of DIY-friendly products, which you can see in our showroom, and we''re happy to give advice and answer any questions you have.\r\n\r\nSiding is like putting together a big puzzle, and it''s even easier with the right guidance from experts who have tackled the challenge before.\r\n\r\nSo what are you waiting for? Get a siding estimate [LINK TO ESTIMATE PAGE], or give us a ring [LINK TO CONTACT PAGE] if you have any questions.', 'DIY Tips', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '60-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-03-16 00:16:57', '2015-03-16 00:16:57', '', 60, 'http://localhost/global-exteriors/60-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
