(914, 1, '2015-03-17 16:44:44', '2015-03-17 16:44:44', 'Whether we’re doing the installation ourselves or helping you DIY, Global Exteriors only offers the best products. We have access to a wide variety of suppliers, tapping Canada’s top brands to outfit your home’s exterior.\r\n<h3>SERVICES</h3>\r\n<div class="services-page">\r\n\r\n<div class="services-grid">\r\n<img src="http://localhost/global-exteriors/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/services-soffit.jpg" alt="services-soffit" />\r\n<div class="services-grid--content"><h5>VINYL SIDING</h5>\r\n<p>The popular choice among today’s consumers, vinyl siding requires little maintenance and is ideal for Saskatchewan’s tough climate.</p>\r\n</div></div>\r\n\r\n<div class="services-grid">\r\n<img src="http://localhost/global-exteriors/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/services-soffit.jpg" alt="services-soffit" />\r\n<div class="services-grid--content"><h5>SOFFIT, FASCIA, AND TRIM</h5>\r\n<p>A vital element to any home’s appearance, our top-quality soffit, fascia, and trim products add that perfect finishing touch.</p>\r\n</div></div>\r\n\r\n<div class="services-grid">\r\n<img src="http://localhost/global-exteriors/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/services-soffit.jpg" alt="services-soffit" />\r\n<div class="services-grid--content"><h5>WINDOWS AND DOORS</h5>\r\n<p>Enhance the look of your home while improving energy efficiency. We can provide any style you want for your home.</p>\r\n</div></div>\r\n\r\n<div class="services-grid">\r\n<img src="http://localhost/global-exteriors/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/services-soffit.jpg" alt="services-soffit" />\r\n<div class="services-grid--content"><h5>EAVESTROUGHS</h5>\r\n<p>All of our eavestroughs are expertly crafted in-house in a wide range of colours and sizes to suit all of your needs.</p>\r\n</div></div>\r\n\r\n<h3>PRODUCTS</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Global Exteriors has access to the best available products through our long standing relationships with our suppliers Gentek, Kaycan, and Mitten.</p>\r\n\r\n<di